All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable, Future<Void>, RunnableFuture<Void>, javafx.concurrent.Worker<Void>, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class ClassificationTask extends javafx.concurrent.Task<Void>
Task that allows executing the classification of sequences in a background thread. This prevents the UI from freezing.
